message.name: Alfred
message.subject: via
message.message: Customer service was on point and the food was out of this world. Every single dish had so much flavour. It was a great experience and we will definitely come back.

message.name: Richard
message.subject: offer
message.message: The views and the atmosphere are breathtaking, the food is spectacular and cooked to perfection. All around just a wonderful place to visit.

message.name: Christine
message.subject: comment
message.message: Everything about our experience was amazing, from pulling up to the valet, to the spectacular views, top notch food, five star service and sounds of the ocean while eating.
